results.best_full_model_response:

  5859 ÷ 3 = 1953, so 5859 = 3 × 1953
  1953 ÷ 3 = 651, so 1953 = 3 × 651
  651 ÷ 3 = 217, so 651 = 3 × 217
  217 = 7 × 31
  So 17577 = 3⁴ × 7 × 31

  13482 ÷ 2 = 6741, so 13482 = 2 × 6741
  6741 ÷ 3 = 2247, so 6741 = 3 × 2247
  2247 ÷ 3 = 749, so 2247 = 3 × 749
  749 = 7 × 107
  So 26964 = 2² × 3³ × 7 × 107

The common factors are 3³ × 7 = 189

- Denominator: 26964 ÷ 189 = 142.6666...

So the GCD is 3² × 7 = 63

Therefore:
